<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Binding components</title>
    <para>
        An ESB will use binding components to integrate with specific service containers, service registries,
        business process execution engines and other components. These will provide the protocol and connectivity
        mapping from the ESB to tha particular component which is bound into an ESB.
    </para>
